{
  "stem": "19690.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had to go through the river and then up an embankment that's about six foot tall-- remember, we're all little-- and then had to climb up that embankment to get to the other side.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The-- the Italian guards that were guarding this border were going to be going to the guardhouse for change of shifts with their dogs.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "When we saw them going away from the border, we are to go closer to the border, inching closer, keeping an eye on the lady.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then when she disappeared, we were going to make a dash.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Meanwhile, we had to look for a hole in the fence to get through.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We-- I had a nine-year-old as my responsibility.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We all had a younger one to take with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So we found a spot and said, the barbed wire is fairly loose there, let's try it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So when the signal came, we made a dash for it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We couldn't see any Swiss guards anywhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we got through the barbed wire a little at a time, getting hung up, tearing our clothes, going a little further.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Then we went into this little river, which in the summer when I saw it again was nothing, but in the spring when the water is melting, it was up to our knees.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We get through the water and here we are up against this high wall, which is higher than I am, that could reach at that time.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, arms came down, grabbing us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It was the Swiss guards that had been lying on their stomachs waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they grabbed us one at a time, pulled us up out of the water and onto land.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
